						               													<description>Seven Waters | a duel of pools&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Anywhere, USA just re-zoned some land, and your dream of building a water park might finally come true! Just your luck, though, that someone else has the exact same idea. Two water parks! What a world. Guess you&amp;rsquo;ll just have to build a bigger and better one. Welcome to Seven Waters!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Overview&amp;#10;Seven Waters is a two-player card-drafting and placement game that can be played with a traditional deck of cards (jokers included). Snag cards from a shared tableau as you attempt to create the most appealing water park, filled with four slides, a lazy river, and a wave pool!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn, you may either (1) draft an available card from a shared pyramid, or (2) play a card from your hand into your water park.  Build water slides by matching the ride value to the rope line value, build a wave pool with matching suits, build a lazy river with straight runs, and theme your park by choosing a bonus value suit.  Best park wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
